smart-retail-platform-2.0/
 ├── config-service         # Centralized Spring Cloud config
 ├── gateway-service        # Spring Cloud Gateway + JWT Auth
 ├── product-service        # Hibernate + Postgres
 ├── order-service          # Async orders + Kafka + Redis cache
 ├── inventory-service      # Optimistic locking + Cassandra
 ├── payment-service        # Secure payment (Stripe API)
 ├── analytics-service      # RxJava + MongoDB + Spark ML
 ├── notification-service   # Reactive emails/SMS (WebFlux)
 ├── fraud-detection        # Python ML (scikit-learn) served via REST
 ├── legacy-integration     # JDBC + SOAP bridge
 ├── frontend-dashboard     # Node.js + React + GraphQL
 └── observability-stack    # Prometheus, Grafana, ELK, Jaeger
